Makefile.am: Make inner class CNI headers depend on libgcj.zip only.

2000-08-03  Bryce McKinlay  <bryce@albatross.co.nz>

	* Makefile.am: Make inner class CNI headers depend on libgcj.zip
	only.
	Fixes "make -j" builds.
	* Makefile.in: Rebuild.

From-SVN: r35441
